flowchart TD
    Start([Start: system prompt plus user message]) --> Build[Build messages list]
    Build --> Call[Call the LLM with messages and TOOL_SCHEMAS]
    Call --> Append[Append the LLM reply to messages]
    Append --> Decide{Did the LLM request tool calls?}
    Decide -- No --> Answer([Return the final answer])
    Decide -- Yes --> Run[Run each requested tool in your code]
    Run --> Results[Append each tool result to messages]
    Results --> Limit{Turn limit reached?}
    Limit -- No --> Call
    Limit -- Yes --> Stop([Return: stopped at turn limit])
